[
    {
        "description": "validation of date-time strings",
        "comment": "RFC 3339 §5.6 date-time format and §5.7 prose constraints. Key rules: month 01-12, day 01-max(month,year) per Gregorian calendar, hour 00-23, minute 00-59, second 00-60 (60 only at a known leap second). T and Z may each be lowercase. -00:00 is valid per §5.2.",
